sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Orchestrator as FMS Guardrails<br/>Orchestrator
    participant Istio as Istio Sidecar<br/>(mTLS)
    participant BuiltIn as Built-in Detector<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant HF as HuggingFace Detector<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant Judge as LLM Judge Detector<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant S3 as S3/MinIO Storage<br/>9000/TCP HTTP
    participant VLLM as vLLM Server<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant KServe as KServe Storage<br/>Initializer

    Note over S3,KServe: Initialization Phase (HuggingFace Detector)
    KServe->>S3: Download model files<br/>HTTP/9000 | AWS credentials
    S3-->>KServe: Model artifacts
    KServe->>HF: Mount model to /mnt/models

    Note over Client,BuiltIn: Flow 1: Built-in Detection (Regex/FileType/Custom)
    Client->>Orchestrator: Inference request
    Orchestrator->>Istio: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>HTTP/8080
    Istio->>BuiltIn: Forward request<br/>mTLS STRICT
    Note right of BuiltIn: Local processing:<br/>regex matching,<br/>file-type parsing,<br/>custom Python execution
    BuiltIn-->>Istio: Detection results
    Istio-->>Orchestrator: Response (mTLS)
    Orchestrator-->>Client: Analysis results

    Note over Client,HF: Flow 2: HuggingFace Model Inference
    Client->>Orchestrator: Inference request
    Orchestrator->>Istio: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>HTTP/8000
    Istio->>HF: Forward request<br/>mTLS STRICT
    Note right of HF: Local PyTorch inference:<br/>tokenize → model forward pass<br/>→ classify/detect spans
    HF-->>Istio: Detection results
    Istio-->>Orchestrator: Response (mTLS)
    Orchestrator-->>Client: Analysis results

    Note over Client,VLLM: Flow 3: LLM Judge Evaluation
    Client->>Orchestrator: Inference request
    Orchestrator->>Istio: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>HTTP/8000
    Istio->>Judge: Forward request<br/>mTLS STRICT
    Judge->>VLLM: OpenAI-compatible API call<br/>HTTP/8080 | No auth
    VLLM-->>Judge: LLM evaluation response
    Judge-->>Istio: Detection results
    Istio-->>Orchestrator: Response (mTLS)
    Orchestrator-->>Client: Analysis results

    Note over BuiltIn,Judge: Prometheus Metrics Scrape
    Note right of BuiltIn: GET /metrics<br/>trustyai_guardrails_*<br/>(detections, requests,<br/>errors, runtime)
